        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Points are awarded based on the following finishing positions</p>
<div style="width: 150px;" class="PodBorder">
<div style="width: 150px;" class="Pod">
<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" style="width: 100%;">
<tbody>
<tr><th colspan="2">Race</th></tr>
<tr><th>Place</th><th>Points</th></tr>
<tr>
<td>1st</td>
<td>25</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2nd</td>
<td>18</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>3rd</td>
<td>15</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4th</td>
<td>12</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>5th</td>
<td>10</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>6th</td>
<td>8</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>7th</td>
<td>6</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>8th</td>
<td>4</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>9th</td>
<td>2</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>10th</td>
<td>1</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<p><br />Points are not awarded for DNF's.  If a car finishes in 10th position according to the in game resutls, but is marked as DNF, no points will be awarded for that car.  Any cars finishing below a car that DNF'd must also have DNF'd and will not be awarded points.  Points will be awarded until the first DNF or through to 10th place.</p>]]></bodyText>
