        <circuitId>14</circuitId>
        <circuitImageAlt>1633</circuitImageAlt>
        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>A high speed test on one of the traditional European circuits, Monza is beloved by the tifosi.  A relatively simple track, the feature points are the Lesmos and the run through Parabolica.  On such a high speed track it's essential to get maximum corner exit speed, so being early on the brakes and early on the throttle, combined with high rolling speed will give a fast lap time.</p>]]></bodyText>
