        <summary><![CDATA[A relative new comer on old shoulders, et_rom_au stamped his presences authoratively on the established midfield and posed a threat to the top order toward the end of season 3.  et_rom_au has shown promising form in the between season testing and is certain to be starting toward the front of the grid and at least challenging for podium finishes.  Possibly the one to watch in season 4.]]></summary>
        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Part of ROM which is Raggedy Old Men which Maverick and I started as a bit of an in joke over 15 years ago. Sadly, we really are Raggedy Old Men now as I'm about to turn 46. I love the challenge that online racing provides. I like to be competitive. I dont intend to sit on the side and just plod around. I want to be challenged and see if I can push others to their limits. Who knows, maybe I can do alright. I'm a courteous driver and if someone is clearly far faster than me, I will yield the track. I guess the point being is that I dont intend to be slower for ever :)</p>]]></bodyText>
