        <teamId>7</teamId>
        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Incorporated by Inidian VJ Malaya, Force India has been a team focussed around one driver, Atomic Lambo.  Since Season 1 it has been 'his' team, and he rewarded Malaya with Atomic F1's first constructors championship in convincing fashion. </p>
<p>Following the departure of Flouncy to Renault at the end of Season 1, Force India took on upcoming driver TurralTerror to give some weight to their constructors championship bid for season 2.</p>
<p><strong>Season 4</strong><br />Sees the first year where Force India has not enlisted the services of it's stalwart Atomic Lambo.  Things may be not be the same for this team now in apparent decline.  Krispy89 has signed with the team but is yet to make an appearance, halfway through the season.</p>]]></bodyText>
