        <teamId>13</teamId>
        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Formed for season 3, following the naming debarcle of Lotus Renault and Team Lotus, Group Force India got in on the act to great success.  Much like the Brawn GP team though, they were short lived.</p>
<p>With Flouncy and HolyGhost79 doing the driving, Group Force India competed in Season 3, winning both the Drivers and Constructors titles, before mysteriously disbanding immediately after their super success.  Flouncy was lured to the undermanned Ferrari, while HolyGhost79 returned to his spiritual home at Team Lotus.</p>]]></bodyText>
