        <teamId>2</teamId>
        <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Born from Jaguar, which was Steward racing, Red Bull F1 are owned by energy drinks magnate Matisich.  Self confessed to be using Formula 1 as a marketing platform, Red Bull have struggled to attract and keep skilled drivers.</p>
<p>Red Bull are optimised for corners, with high performing aerodynamics developed by the worlds best, Adrian Newey.</p>
<p>Red Bull need to find a top line driver if they are to move forward.</p>
<p><strong>Season 4<br /></strong>Entered with two drivers but left with one after notjedi was dropped after only one race.  New-comer st8smn350 tries hard, but they have struggled to be competitive and without an experienced driver to take the team foward they likely not pose a threat.</p>
<p><strong>Season 1 <br /></strong>Started the season with Krispy89 and OriginalBollum, but ended with only one driver, Krispy89, who performed admirably.<strong><br /></strong></p>]]></bodyText>
