              <metaTitle>
              </metaTitle>
              <metaKeywords><![CDATA[]]></metaKeywords>
              <metaDescription><![CDATA[]]></metaDescription>
              <thumbnail>
              </thumbnail>
              <teaser><![CDATA[]]></teaser>
              <content><![CDATA[<p>"As long as I win the next four races and Lambo comes last in each of them, the title is there for the taking. For sure it's no walk in the park, but after today's races Vijay told me he was going to get behind me and really give it to me. So I'm optimistic about a new front wing, or something."<br /> <br /> With the season taking a brief hiatus, drivers have retired to various boats in the Mediterranean for some of that hot chicky action F1 stars are famous for, and a pole fight with Kimi.</p>]]></content>
