              <content><![CDATA[<p>It was clear from the outset of the Spanish Atomic F1 GP that the majority of the teams and drivers had been practicing this track.  Lines were tidy and times were low.  Spain saw the re-introduction of Season 1 racer bobaj0r, returning from his stint in NASCAR to join the cast of regulars.</p>
<p>Qualifying was pretty much as expected with Flouncy taking first place from TurrbalTerror, HolyGhost79, Atomic Lambo, bobabj0r, OriginalBollum, Fredzfrog and a rapidly improving BreakerMorant.</p>
<?UMBRACO_MACRO type="Qualifying" macroAlias="F1InlineRace" raceid="9" />
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Race highlights</strong></p>
<?UMBRACO_MACRO utubewidth="480" utubevideo="QElr5qQ8sZM" utubeheight="360" macroAlias="uTube.ChromelessPlayer" />
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p>As the pack left the start grid it appeared someone had forgot to tell TurrbalTerror there was a race on, as he stood on the grid while all but Mac Dude drove around him.  TurrbalTerror later reported a clutch problem on his Mclaren. After the first few laps TurrbalTerror had regained ground.  Having dispatched Fredzfrog and OriginalBollum by turn 4 of lap 1 he stuck to the back of bobaj0r and Atomic Lambo while Ghost and Flouncy opened a small gap.  A few laps in and Atomic Lambo had a slip on the astro-turf, letting bobaj0r go and TurrbalTerror go past.</p>
<p>TurrbalTerror caught up to Flouncy, where they battled for a few laps, exchanging places as each pushed the other a little too hard.  On lap 8 TurrbalTerror spun on the final corner and damaged his front wing, immediately pitting for repairs.</p>
<p>Both Atomic Lambo and TurrbalTerror pushed hard to catch the leading pack and both spun on a number of occasions, eventually settling for 4<sup>th</sup> and 3<sup>rd</sup> places respectively.</p>
<p>Final Race results saw HolyGhost lead Flouncy, TurrbalTerror, Atomic Lambo, bobaj0r, OriginalBollum, FredzFrog, and BreakerMorant</p>
<?UMBRACO_MACRO type="Race" macroAlias="F1InlineRace" raceid="9" />
<p> </p>]]></content>
