              <thumbnail>
              </thumbnail>
              <teaser><![CDATA[]]></teaser>
              <content><![CDATA[<p>The last two grand prix held at Istanbul Park have had the same podium and there's little to indicate this race will be any different.  In both races, Flouncy, HolyGhost79, and Atomic Lambo have occupied the top three spots, with current fourth place in the championship, TurrbalTerror 6th and 5th. </p>
<p>It is expect that pole position will be fought out between HolyGhost79 and Flouncy with 2nd row of the grid occupied by Atomic Lambo and bobaj0r.  Spirits are high at Group Force India after recent success and a convinving lead in the constructors championship.  Their latest addition to the steering and front end geometery on the #1 car will only help Flouncy in his quest for his second pole positition of the year.</p>
<p>Toward the less experienced end of the grid, Mac Dude is showing impressive improvements and is already raising eyebrows further up the grid as those teams look to seek new blood to improve their prospects. </p>
<p>One such team is McLaren, who are reportedly unhappy with the performance of TurrbalTerror and looking to promote bobaj0r to team leader and offload TurrbalTerror for season 4.  Things don't look good in the TurrbalTerror camp, as raw pace is not being converted to race points, through poor car control and setup decisions.</p>]]></content>
