              <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/2821/g27.jpg" width="150" height="150" alt="g27.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 20px;"/>McLaren CEO Rob Gray reports Team McLaren will install the Logitech G27 steering upgrade to  bobaj0r's car in time for the Valenica GP this weekend.  Gray said "This will greatly help stabilise the equilbrium within the team dynamic and bring compounding synergies to the team at a time when we're focusing on driving forward and meeting stakeholder objectives".  </p>
<p>bobaj0r is excited to be testing the upgrade at Thursday evening's test session.</p>]]></content>
