              <content><![CDATA[<p>Back in the dawn of the atomic f1 championship, we were blessed with one of the most skillful pilots to grace the track, Eradicator84.  Using an Xbox controller, he managed to not only compete, but to shame his fellow competitors who were using more advanced steering devices (wheels), clinching podiums and the occasional victory in the process.</p>
<p>While Season 1 started very strongly, we saw a fading Eradicator84 in season 2, as he all to often fell back into the middle of the pack, the best of the rest.  He still had fight left in him though and run of podiums at the end of the season ensure he wouldn't leave the sport in disgrace.</p>
<p>Officially on sabatical from Season 3, it's hoped Eradicator84 makes a return to fulltime racing in Season 4 and comes back as strong as ever.  His return will do nothing but increase the strength of the field and give aspiring front runners a glimmer of hope that the seemingly impossible can be achieved in inferior equipment.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Check out his fantastic record (4th best ever!) <a href="/{localLink:1271}" title="Eradicator84">here</a></p>]]></content>
