              <metaDescription><![CDATA[The second out of season race was run last night, to fantastic success, at the Honda owned Suzuka circuit in Japan.  We had 10 starters, made up of some first times, st8tsmann and notjedi, as well as some occasional oldies such as bushipoo, and recent newbies like CruiserComet, as well as stalwarts Flouncy, HolyGhost79, and TurrbalTerror, and more.  ]]></metaDescription>
