              <teaser><![CDATA[After the resounding success of the 100% distance out of season events, the race distance for season 4 has been extended from 40% to 100%.]]></teaser>
              <content><![CDATA[<p>After the resounding success of the 100% distance out of season events, the race distance for season 4 has been extended from 40% to 100%.  To accomodate this increased distance only 1 race per race weekend will be held. The same 15 minute qualifying session will be used.</p>
<p>Having 1 race per weekend will give drivers and teams the chance to focus on one track during practice each week.  It will also give the opportunity to midfield drivers to make up places if they make mistakes or get punted early on in the race.</p>
<p>It will make the season longer, but for those not able to compete in a full season, they can participate as motivation allows. </p>]]></content>
