              <content><![CDATA[<p>The third and final out-of-season race before season 4 kicks off with F1 2011 in October is Istanbul.  Like the other out of season races, this is a 100% distance race and all the driver aids are available should you choose to use them.</p>
<p>The race will be held at 7pm, this Sunday August 21.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><img src="~/media/15990/istanbul-park_398x264.jpg"  width="398"  height="264" alt="Istanbul -park" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"/></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Season 3 saw the closest grid in the history of the atomic f1 competition, so this race is sure to be competitive, as everyone strives to win the last race using F1 2010. </p>
<?UMBRACO_MACRO type="Qualifying" macroAlias="F1InlineRace" raceid="11" />
<p> </p>
<p>Since that race we've got a number of new-comers with plenty of performance, including the ROManians, and CruiserComet, st8tsmann and more.  All will be keen to have crack at the established drivers.</p>]]></content>
