              <content><![CDATA[<p><?UMBRACO_MACRO videoheight="" aspectratio="" macroAlias="uTube.ClassicPlayer" videoid="7xWQFFQolRA" videourl="" videowidth="640" allowfullscreen="0" />
<p> </p>
<p>Atomic F1 Championship registrations for season 4 are now open.  The first race has been announced for the Albert Park circuit in Melbourne, to be held at 8pm October 9th, Sydney time (EDST, GMT +11).</p>
<p>To nonimate, follow the links from our <a href="/{localLink:1599}" title="Join">Join</a> page and specify your team and name.  See the front page of the site in the "Drivers Standings" for a list of people currently enrolled.  This can also be found in the first post of the main thread.</p></p>]]></content>
