              <teaser><![CDATA[There is a defect in the F1 2011 regulation ECU that gives an extreme handling performance boost.]]></teaser>
              <content><![CDATA[<p>There is a defect in the F1 2011 regulation ECU that gives an extreme handling performance boost when front and rear springs are set to 11 (maximum).  There is a gentlemans agreement in place for the F1 2011 competition that springs at 11 will not be used. </p>
<p>While usage can't be policed, we hope that no competitors will use this setting.  We're all familiar with each others ability anyway ;)</p>]]></content>
