              <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="~/media/21037/driver-face_200x133.jpg"  width="200"  height="133" alt="driver-face.PNG" style="float: right;"/>Fresh new driver talent <a href="/{localLink:1705}" title="Modz">Modz</a> has signed for the Sauber team effective immediately. </p>
<p>Peter Sauber made the announcement in front of a small press gathering at 9:53pm this evening.  Modz has come up from the junior formulae is excited about making the leap up Atomic F1 championship, itself a thriving a continually growing championship. </p>
<p>All drivers are excited by this news, especially compatriot and fellow racer CruiserComet.  Double world champion Flouncy offered a warm welcome to the driver, as long as he kept his nose clean and away from Flouncy's exhaust in China.</p>
<p>The addition of Modz completes the grid of 16 full time races, and one reserve driver in Krispy89.</p>]]></content>
