              <teaser><![CDATA[Secret footage has been obtain of a secret Mclaren test at Silverstone and all is not well at Woking]]></teaser>
              <content><![CDATA[<p><?UMBRACO_MACRO videourl="" videoid="Ug70WdE7si8" aspectratio="" videoheight="" macroAlias="uTube.ClassicPlayer" videowidth="" allowfullscreen="0" />
<p></p>
<p>Recently received from an anonymous source, spy footage of a secret Mclaren test at Silverstone reveal the constructors championship leaders are struggling with pace and balance as they work feverishly on preparations for this weekends British Grand Prix at Silverstone.</p>
<p>From the footage obtained Mclaren can clearly be seen spinning on a number of occassions as TurrbalTerror tries to hone in on a setup. </p>
<p>From the evidence on this footage, Mclaren have a long way to go and the other nearby teams look sure to snare a rare race win unless preparations take a drastic turn for the better for the Woking based team.</p></p>]]></content>
