    <umbTextpage id="1599" parentID="1084" level="2" writerID="0" creatorID="0" nodeType="1055" template="1836" sortOrder="15" createDate="2011-08-16T12:55:08" updateDate="2012-01-12T09:50:00" nodeName="Join" urlName="join" writerName="Rob Gray" creatorName="Rob Gray" path="-1,1084,1599" isDoc="">
      <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Ever wanted to race in a Formula 1?  Can't afford it? Here's the next best thing, the Atomic F1 championship, run on cheap PC hardware, using Codemasters F1 2011 game.</p>
<p>We're a group of racing and Formula 1 enthusiasts who welcome new additions to our league, providing everyone is friendly.  There's no need to race in every event. Join up and race when it suits you (providing there's a race on).  If you're more keen, and we're sure you will be, turn up for every race and fight for championship glory.</p>
<p>Perhaps you're not ready yet or not sure what you're getting yourself in to? Read our <a title="Rookie Guide to racing in the Atomic F1 championship" href="/{localLink:1312}">rookie guide</a> to get a better idea. We also have a "Concorde Agreement" that spells out the rules of the competition.  Check it out <a title="Atomic F1 Season 4 Concorde Agreement" href="/{localLink:1658}">here</a>.</p>
<p>Please include your Windows Live For Games ID in your message.</p>]]></bodyText>
